    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents a rare opportunity to own a mechanically flawless example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies, with the Double-VANOS system operating within factory tolerances for precise valve timing. The longitudinal Getrag 6-speed manual is paired with a limited-slip M-Variable differential, offering exceptional power delivery and mechanical grip. Every suspension component, from the front MacPherson struts to the multi-link rear, remains taut with no bushing fatigue. The subframe has been meticulously inspected and reinforced, addressing the chassis's primary known vulnerability. The exterior finish is concours-standard, showing no signs of track use or environmental degradation. This is a turn-key, investment-quality vehicle for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
