      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-ready condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and pampered by a single owner. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster with absolutely zero imperfections, while the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every surface, from the supple, uncreased leather seats to the pristine dashboard, reflects a life of careful preservation. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting its flawless upkeep. With exceptionally low mileage and a smooth, whisper-quiet ride, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. No stains, no scratches, no compromises\u2014just pure, unadulterated excellence for the discerning collector.",
